# name: test_render_table_appends_drift_section_when_present
  '''
  verify host=h1 user=ops at=2026-06-09T12:00:00Z
    summary: clean=0 expected_fail=0 new_fail=0 regression=1 incomplete=0 — FAILURES
  
    CATEGORY    CURRENT  INSTALL  EXP  RULE
    regression  fail     pass     no   rule_b
  
  Tailoring drift detected — workstation host.yaml differs from /root/tailoring.xml.
  Re-run `ks-gen gen <host.yaml>` and redeploy to align.
  
    + disable rule_x
    - select rule_y
    ~ rule_z: 5 → 24
    (profile changed: profile_b → profile_a)
  
  '''
